</h3><h4 id="场景1-索引列参与计算">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#%e5%9c%ba%e6%99%af1-%e7%b4%a2%e5%bc%95%e5%88%97%e5%8f%82%e4%b8%8e%e8%ae%a1%e7%ae%97"></a>
